                        p.text-sm.md:text-base.text-gray-600.mt-2.mb-0
                            | A single Swift file you can drop into a macOS app target. Handles the headless install/uninstall flow, install and running detection, and posts the show/hide notifications.
                    a.btn.text-black.bg-rose-200.hover:text-black.hover:bg-rose-300.rounded-lg.flex.justify-center.items-center.border-rose-300.border-2.shrink-0 href="https://gist.github.com/alin23/69c0b52b03ab68e3b238ff4ef0f6fde7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
