                        .font-semibold Your app must `strong.text-900 not` be sandboxed
                        div The App Sandbox blocks most operations the integration relies on:
                        ul.list-disc.pl-5.space-y-1
                            li Writing `code Keylume.app` to `code /Applications`
                            li Posting `code DistributedNotificationCenter` notifications
                            li Setting `code UserDefaults` on the `code com.lowtechguys.Keylume` suite

                .free-note.flex.items-start.gap-3.bg-sky-100.border-2.border-sky-300.rounded-lg.p-4
